  "description": "<p>Map of Anchorage, Alaska. Made using the Map Patcher by Kronifer and US Demand Generator by slurry.</p>\n<p>Note: 2016 LODES data was used since this was the most recent data available. Since the population of Anchorage hasn't changed much since then, the data should be accurate enough.</p>\n\n<p>Additional demand data as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Airports: Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport (ANC)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Universities: University of Alaska Anchorage</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Entertainment/Tourism: Anchorage Museum, Alaska Native Historical Center, Alaska Zoo, Stadium District</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Military Bases: Joint Base Elmendorf-Richardson (split into 9 demand points)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
